Title: To the Meadery
Description:
Your archer friend is right. We must eliminate Zirix and his forces if the Coreway is to remain safe.

Let us head to the Cinderbrew Meadery at once.
ObjectivesText: Meet Baelgrim at the Cinderbrew Meadery.
RewardText: Thank the titans! The nerubians have not made their move to take the mead yet.
